Package: pathdb
Type: Package
Title: pathdb: A Comprehensive Database for Pathway Enrichment Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Aidan", "Frederick",
      email = "aidanfred24@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: pathdb is a comprehensive R package for pathway enrichment analysis that provides access to large-scale genomics data from the South Dakota State University's bioinformatics database to provide a unified platform for pathway analysis of over 13,000 organisms. It includes various gene mappings, gene characteristics, and pathway mapping data from KEGG, GOBP, GOCC, and many more pathway databases. This package also provides various helper functions for processing RNA-Seq data for differential expression analysis and pathway enrichment analysis.
